That still isn't working great... here is the confluence page set up and the CSS with it:

/**************************************** Expand Macro - People Team (from SASConnect)***************************************/
.drop .expand-control-text, .drop2 .expand-control-text {
color: black !important; / Change text color */
text-decoration: none !important;
font-size: 17px !important;
font-family: SamsungOneBold !important;
}

.drop .aui-button .aui-icon, .drop2 .aui-button .aui-icon {
color: #1428a0 !important; /* Change icon color /
vertical-align: middle !important; / Aligns the icon vertically with the text /
margin-right: 8px !important; / Adds some space between the icon and the text */
}

.drop .aui-button.aui-button-link, .drop2 .aui-button.aui-button-link {
color: black !important; /* Change link color */
text-decoration: none !important;
}

/* Wrap long expand macro title text for /
.drop .expand-control button.aui-button.aui-button-link.aui-button-link-icon-text, .drop2 .expand-control button.aui-button.aui-button-link.aui-button-link-icon-text {
text-align: left !important; / Aligns the button text to the left /
white-space: normal !important; / Ensures the text wraps normally /
overflow-wrap: break-word !important; / Allows long words to be broken and wrapped onto the next line /
display: flex !important; / Uses flexbox to align items /
align-items: flex-start !important; / Vertically centers the icon and text /
justify-content: flex-start !important; / Ensures the button content starts at the beginning */
}

/* Apply Samsung font & background to content within the expand /
.drop .expand-content, .drop2 .expand-content {
width: 100% !important; / Ensures the expand content takes up the full width of its container /
box-sizing: border-box !important; / Includes padding and border in the element's total width and height */
background-color: #f8f8f8;
font-family: SamsungOne;
font-size: 16px;
}

/* Makes the grey background on the content within the expand the width of the page /
.drop .expand-content {
margin: 0 1720px 10px 20px !important; / Large right margin */
padding: 16px 17px 15px 15px !important;
}

/* Adds a top margin to the content within the expand /
.drop2 .expand-content {
margin: 65px 0 10px 20px !important; / Creates space between the long expand title and the content */
padding: 16px 17px 15px 15px !important;
}

/* Changing color of links in the expand content and added a dotted line under the link */
.drop .sas-element-accordian-link a, .drop .sas-element-accordian-link a:link, .drop2 .sas-element-accordian-link a, .drop2 .sas-element-accordian-link a:link{
border-bottom: 1px dotted !important;
color: #1428a0 !important;
}

/* Setting the color & font weight when the link is hovered over */
.drop .sas-element-accordian-link a:hover, .drop2 .sas-element-accordian-link a:hover {
font-weight: normal !important;
color: #0077C8 !important;
}

/* Removing the underline when the expand text is hovered over */
.drop .expand-control-text:hover, .drop2 .expand-control-text:hover, .drop .aui-button.aui-button-link.aui-button-link-icon-text:hover, .drop2 .aui-button.aui-button-link.aui-button-link-icon-text:hover, .drop .aui-button-link:focus, .drop2 .aui-button-link:focus {
text-decoration: none !important;
}

